OL,3,CSMA explained: The rare genetic
OL,4,Ccondition affecting Jesy Nelson's twins
OL,6,FFormer Little Mix singer Jesy Nelson
OL,7,Fhas said her twin babies are unlikely
OL,8,Fto ever be able to walk after being
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with a rare condition.
OL,11,FThe 34-year-old, who gave birth
OL,12,Fprematurely to Ocean Jade and Story
OL,13,FMonroe Nelson-Foster in May with her
OL,14,Ffiance, Zion Foster, said the twins
OL,15,Fhave been diagnosed with type 1 spinal
OL,16,Fmuscular atrophy (SMA).
