OL,3,CSMA explained: The rare genetic
OL,4,Ccondition affecting Jesy Nelson's twins
OL,6,FSpinal muscular atrophy (SMA) is a
OL,7,Frare genetic condition that causes
OL,8,Fmuscle weakness, according to the NHS.
OL,10,FIt gets worse over time, but medicines
OL,11,Fand other treatments can help manage
OL,12,Fsymptoms.
OL,14,FWhat are the different types of SMA?
OL,16,FSMA is usually grouped into four main
OL,17,Ftypes, based on what age the symptoms
OL,18,Fbegin and how they affect sitting,
OL,19,Fstanding and walking.
