OL,3,CSMA explained: The rare genetic
OL,4,Ccondition affecting Jesy Nelson's twins
OL,6,FThe NHS says SMA affects everyone
OL,7,Fdifferently. Some types are more
OL,8,Fsevere and can affect life expectancy.
OL,10,FIn general, the earlier symptoms
OL,11,Fbegin, the more serious the condition
OL,12,Fis likely to be, though outcomes
OL,13,Fdepend on individual symptoms and how
OL,14,Fwell treatment works.
