OL,3,CSMA explained: The rare genetic
OL,4,Ccondition affecting Jesy Nelson's twins
OL,6,FIf a doctor suspects a child may have
OL,7,FSMA, the condition can be confirmed
OL,8,Fwith a blood test, according to the
OL,9,FNHS.
OL,11,FPeople who may be at risk of having a
OL,12,Fchild with SMA can be referred by
OL,13,Ftheir GP to a genetic counsellor to
OL,14,Fdiscuss risks and options.
