OL,6,FThe scheme is a two-year pilot, funded
OL,7,Fby the Scottish Government and
OL,8,Fpharmaceutical company Novartis, that
OL,9,Fwill see infants born in Scotland
OL,10,Fscreened for the condition as part of
OL,11,Fthe existing blood spot test when they
OL,12,Fare just five days old.
OL,14,FCountries including France, Germany,
OL,15,FRussia, Norway, Sweden and Turkey have
OL,16,Falready introduced nationwide SMA
OL,17,Fblood spot testing for newborns.
